Quagliarella to Sky: &quot;My advice to Donnarumma is to stay and become a symbol at Milan, because they believed in him when he was a kid.&quot;<br />
<br />
A group of members of the Curva Sud laid out a banner in front of Casa Milan saying: &quot;We don't accept blackmailing... go on like this Milan&quot;

Ricardo Rodriguez: &quot;Milan is a big club and we want to get back to the top. I don't have an idol, but I always watched Milan matches.&quot;<br />
<br />
Ricardo Rodriguez: &quot;3 is my favourite number. I also like 13 and 33, but I'm not thinking about that at the moment. I'll choose later.&quot;
